                "invention-title": [
                    "Synthesis method of high-purity silicon carbide raw material",
                    "一种高纯碳化硅原料的合成方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to the field of synthesis of a high-purity silicon carbide raw material for silicon carbide single crystal growth, in particular to a synthesis method of the high-purity silicon carbide raw material, which comprises the following steps of: 1, putting silicon particles or silicon blocks serving as a silicon source into a bottom area of an inner crucible, putting blocky graphite serving as a carbon source into a bottom area of a cavity defined by the inner crucible and an outer crucible, placing the outer crucible in a synthetic furnace, vacuumizing a furnace chamber, heating to 1000-1300 DEG C, and keeping the temperature for 5-10 hours; and 2, introducing a mixed gas of hydrogen and argon in a ratio of 5-10% into the furnace chamber, raising the temperature of the furnace chamber to 2200-2500 DEG C, and reacting for 5-10 hours to obtain the silicon carbide raw material. According to the method, the high-purity silicon carbide raw material which is suitable for growth of the high-purity semi-insulating silicon carbide crystal and has few nitrogen impurities can be obtained under the condition of relatively low cost."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及碳化硅单晶生长用高纯碳化硅原料合成领域，具体涉及一种高纯碳化硅原料的合成方法，包括以下步骤：步骤一，硅粒或者硅块为硅源放入内坩埚的底部区域，块状石墨为碳源放入内坩埚与外坩埚所围成空腔的底部区域，并将所述外坩埚置于合成炉中，将炉腔抽真空后升温至1000～1300℃，恒温5～10小时；步骤二，向炉腔中通入氢气比例为5％～10％的氢气与氩气的混合气体后，将炉腔温度升至2200～2500℃，反应5～10小时，得到碳化硅原料。通过本发明可以在成本较低的情况下获得适用于高纯半绝缘碳化硅晶体生长的氮杂质少的高纯度的碳化硅原料。"
                }
            ]
        }
